Silent Remedy App

*Silent Remedy App* is an application designed to automatically manage the phone's sound profile. The app disables the "silent" mode when receiving a call from a favorite contact and automatically re-enables it after the call ends.

## Features
- Automatically disable silent mode when receiving a call from a favorite contact.
- Automatically re-enable silent mode after the call ends.
- Customizable favorite contact list.
- Utilizes Flutter libraries to manage call state and audio settings.

## Requirements
- *Flutter 2.0+*
- *Android SDK* (supports Android 5.0 and above)
- *Phone Permissions*: The app requires READ_PHONE_STATE and MODIFY_AUDIO_SETTINGS permissions
